FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our toilet paper marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the toilet paper marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects toilet paper buyers with sellers, allowing you to browse, compare, and purchase various toilet paper products from different vendors all in one place.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What types of toilet paper can I find on the marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We offer a wide range of toilet paper products, including recycled, ultra-soft, quilted, scented, and bulk options from various brands and independent sellers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How do I know if a seller is reliable?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Each seller on our marketplace has a rating and review system. You can check their feedback from previous customers to ensure you're buying from a reputable source.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: What if I'm not satisfied with my toilet paper purchase?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We have a customer-friendly return policy. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund or exchange.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do you offer bulk purchasing options for businesses?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, we cater to both individual consumers and businesses. We offer bulk purchasing options with competitive pricing for companies looking to stock up on toilet paper supplies.
